gitlab-rake restore   ------------>internally works
       │
       ├── 1) Stop GitLab services (NOT PostgreSQL)
       ├── 2) Extract backup tar
       ├── 3) Check version compatibility
       ├── 4) Drop + Recreate database
       ├── 5) Restore SQL file into PostgreSQL
       ├── 6) Restore repositories
       ├── 7) Restore uploads, artifacts, registry
       ├── 8) Reconfigure GitLab
       │
       └── GitLab comes online with restored data

